variables.value: Muscles are everything! Right?!\nLet's master the flex together!
If you're recruiting, no thanks.\nI'm busy, so kindly step aside.
Why can't you see the beauty?\nWhat's life without muscles?!
I still have room to improve!\nHow do I train the brain muscle?
As long as humans have muscles...\nThere's hope you'll understand one day.
Fool! Why must you deny the\nwonders of muscles?!
Nice pectorals... Oh! Sorry!\nInterested in the Judo Club?
Not interested—at all.\nJust leave me alone.
What?! You cheeky little—!\nYou won't get away next time!
You dare deny the sweet sweat of youth?!
Ah, the joy of throwing, and being\nthrown! Ignorance is sin!
Why can't you see?!\nWeight is essential to life!
Sumo, our national sport!\nStep into the ring! Boo-yah!
I'll pass.\nPlease find someone else.
You'll come to love it!\nFlesh against flesh—pure beauty.
Why are you sprinkling salt around?\nThere's nothing to purify here!
You dare deny the beauty of\nbattle-born bodies?!
Whaaat?!\nHands off the sacred pot!
Let us reach for the cosmos!
I have no interest in space.
Huh? No interest at all?
Oof. When you put it like that...
Look at you...\nActing all high and mighty.
You're from Class A, right?\nDo you have Miss <LST:KASUMISAKI>'s number?
Miss <LST:KASUMISAKI>'s number...?\nYeah, no—I can't help you there.
Guess I'm on my own...\nStill, I have butterflies in my stomach.
She'll probably turn me down...\nBut I've gotta try!
You've got a certain flair...\nThe potential of "P"!
The potential of "P?" What even is that?\nSounds lame.
Fine... I'll back off for now.\nBut you're joining... eventually!
OMG, how could you say that?!\nOur values sure differ...
Don't tell me—that you're actually\nan industry insider?!
You'll volunteer, won't you?\nFor the campus cleanup?
That's what this is about?\nSorry, I'm swamped.
That's too bad.\nHope you can join us next time!
Seriously?!\nI'm the one who needs cleaning up?!
No way! Are you telling me\nwe don't need a cleanup?!
It's true that you should always\nstart with yourself...
You look free!\nMind modeling for one of my sketches?
I'm not really into art.\nCan't you ask someone else?
Oh, you're busy? \nLet me know if you're ever free.
Wh-what do you mean?\nArtistic expression matters, but...
C-cut it out, you're scaring me!
By "friend," you mean it\nliterally, right?
Hi! Do you have a moment?\nWe're with the school paper!
Sorry, no time.\nWhy not try someone else?
Dodging questions, huh?\nI'll get the scoop next time!
Wait... don't tell me—\nyou're a walking red flag?!
C'mon, let's be friends!
Phew... Gotta lose him.
Ignoring me?! That's ice cold!\nBut you're not getting away!
Huh? Was I too pushy?\nI didn't mean it like that...
Out here this late?\nSomething bothering you?
Something on your mind?\nCome, tell me about it.
I'm fine, really.\nNo need for advice.
No fortune today?\nWhat a curious child.
Truly? No worries?\nNo curiosity about the future?
Hey, kid, out at this hour?\nYou're coming down to the station!
I'm just out for a walk, sir.\nMy parents said it's fine.
Is my sense of justice...\nnot enough?
Call the cops on me?!\nI'm just standing up for justice...
Ugh... Hic! Heeey, kiddo!\nC'mere, lend me an ear!
Ew, he reeks of booze...\nI gotta get out of here.
What's with the sour face?!\nBeat it, will ya?!
Huh? Hic!\nThat's a real blast from the past, kiddo.
Whoa?! Was I really trying to drag a\nminor into the vile world of alcohol?
That hairstyle's not permitted.\nFix it by tomorrow.
That can't be right.\nAren't you being a little picky?
...I'll let it slide today.\nBut next time, no excuses!
Why you little...!\nYou're gonna regret this!
Oh, that's a good point...
Ouch! That kinda hurt my feelings!
That uniform of yours...\nButton it up properly!
Do you have to be\nso strict about all this?
I'll let it slide this time.\nBut you better show some school pride!
Oh yeah? At least we're not the ones\nsticking out like sore thumbs!
Oh, I see what you mean...
Oof! You really rubbed salt onto\nmy wounds with that one...
Meow meow meow...!\n(You won't win meowver that easily!)
C'mon, let's get you home.\nHuh, maybe she hates me.
Meow meow meow, mreoow!\n(Fine, you may escort meow!)
Meow meow, mreoooww!\n(Such a meowthwatering scent!)
Meow meow meown, meow!\n(What a purrfect massage!)
Here comes the <FUL:UMIBOZU>!\nI'm back in <FUL:UMIKTION>!
The <FUL:UMIBOZU>? Smells fishy...\nWhat's going on here?
<FUL:BO>! Let me swim freely!
<FUL:UMI>! I'm in deep water now!\nIt's time to dip!
I... seem to be lost.\nCould you show me the way?
I can't just leave her.\nShe clearly needs help.
Thank you, dear.\nYou're very kind.
My, such a gentleman!\nI'll gladly accept your offer.
You've got the look of a noodle lover!\nCome on, dig in!
I'm not...\nStop assuming stuff!
But I'm in the mood for it...
If you insist...\nguess I've got no choice.
What do you mean?!\nMy udon lost to Champon...?
You're still growing, aren't you?\nI'll supersize it on the house!
No thanks.\nYou can keep the supersize.
You're pretty reserved...\nI'll whip up your favorite next time.
If you say so...\nI won't push it.
Health comes first?! What a shame.
Can you distract my brother?\nHe won't stop tailing me!
My sister's totally clueless—\nshe needs me to keep her safe!
Why drag me into this?\nI'm just some random passerby.
Geez, you're so clingy!
He's right!\nNow I'm off to find a boyfriend!
Told you so! I knew it!
Personal space is important,\neven for siblings.
I'm just looking out for you!\nHey—don't walk away!
Huh? That's the plan?\nThat's just as bad!
But I'm your brother!\nIt's normal for me to be worried!
That's why I'm sticking to\nproper sibling boundaries!
Stop! Don't touch that ball! The\nDark Society could've tampered with it!
What in the world...?
You didn't take the bait...\nSociety truly is a cautious creature.
You think I'm scared of my mom?\nYeah, right!
W-waaah! I'm sorry!
Don't get cocky, punks!\nThis is payback for yesterday!
These guys are society's trash.\nAnd today's garbage day.
Remember, you asked for this.\nWe're not gonna hold back.
Dang it! They're just kids!\nAlright—fall back for now!
Grgh! These brats are\nwiping the floor with us!
Hey!\nWhat kind of lecture was that?!
Well, what have we here?\nA few runts up for a challenge?
Time for Hecaton Stairway training!\nLet's go!
Looks like a whole different\nbeast from the usual.
Let's just get this over with...
Return whenever you dare,\nO brave young challengers.
Not bad, kids.\nWe shall meet again.
Come on, it's not over yet.
Oof...
Gimme a breather...
You can't, not yet.
Haaa, haaa... I'm beat.
This isn't something you do on the way home...
I've been wanting to try it.
I think we can quickly improve if we\ntrain during school hours.
If it's come to this... I'll finish\nyou myself! Final form—activate!
We're gonna unravel the mystery!\nLet's go, guys!
You sure about this?\nWe won't get cursed, will we?
The <FUL:UMIBOZU>, for real?\nI'd rather not deal with it...
Gah! You got me!\n—Wait, a malfunction?
Huh? Did it break?
It's a clash for control—\nwho'll own the midfield...?
Who do you think I am?
Now do you get it?
What just happened...?
No way... This can't be real...
Tch... All bark, huh?
Report me to the council, and I'll\nrelease your most embarrassing photos.
It's not as if\nwe've got anything to hide.
Ju-just as I predicted.
Ugh... I can't help it. I can't resist\nanalyzing everyone I see...
This looks fun! Count me in!
C'mon! Bring it on!
Whew! You satisfied now?
Yeah... that was a blast.
Air football or not, take it seriously!
...Got it.
Dude's a total wrestling freak!\nYou're toast!
Be it pro wrestling or sumo,\nI'll take you on!
W-What?!\nThis isn't the finale?!
Why?! Dang it! His kicks...\nthey're getting even sharper!
You think you can take us?\nFine, we'll play along.
I can already see it—\nthe future where you lose.
Dang it...\nWe really lost to these runts...
We're mutts...?\nBut everyone's terrified of us!
You expect us to join those\nwho merely admire space?
Though your love differs,\nyou all cherish the same universe.
...Very well.\nI understand your position.
We must elevate our\nawareness to a cosmic scale...
I live for the stars' glow!\nJoin those who would taint them? Never.
Feelings about the night sky are as\nvaried as the stars themselves.
Admiration is not the\nsole expression of love...
So you're saying... To speak of beauty,\none must grasp its essence.
Think you're heroes, eh?
Only scrubs talk like that.
Just who are you guys...?
I ain't losing to hero wannabes!
<LST:YAGYU> belongs on the diamond!\nAnd it's your fault he's not!
*Sigh*...\nDelusional fans are the worst.
Wh-What...?\nWe were wrong...?
S-So that makes us...\nfake fans?!
We need a neutral voice. The swimming\nclub deserves first splash, right?
We've got a big match coming!\nNo way we're backing off!
This quarrel is none of my concern.\nKindly exclude me.
I'll let you float... for now.
Don't think we'll bend to you next time!
Coming from you... that hits deep.
Looks like it's sink or swim now!
Your eyes lack spark!\nTime to cheer!
No. This is just how I look.
Ever in need of a boost?\nJust give us a shout!
That fire in your eyes...\nGuess our work here's done.
We'd be popular if you guys\nweren't stealing the spotlight!
That's quite the projection...
Don't forget! <MNT:NAGUMOHARA> hoops—\nfighting for fame and love!
Quit making us sound like thirst goblins!
Give me some love for my latest work!\nNo hate, okay?
Sounds like you just want praise.
All I wanted was a little praise...\nI'll show you my next one soon!
Ow!\nThat hit deep!
We need a proper resort!\nPlease sign our redevelopment petition!
Why drag me into this?\nI'm just some random passerby.
Everyone loves a resort,\nstubborn kid.
...You're right.\nI've been narrow-minded.
Studying's your duty as a student!
No thanks. I'm good.
Sure you don't want in?\nWe'll be here!
Thinking that far ahead...?!\nNow that's focus.
A little malnourished, are we?\nOne smoothie to solve it all!
I'm not really in the mood.
No smoothie?\nWell, if you change your mind...
...You do seem like someone\nwith plenty of room to grow.
You think winning's enough?\nThat's just naive.
What are you implying?
What?! Ignoring my advice?!\nYou'll regret that!
Gah... I didn't mean that!
I'm on an autograph hunt.\nYours is next, come on!
You're not supposed to be here.\nSlip out before you're caught.
Stingy much?\nI'm not giving up!
I-I'm not some poser,\nokay?!
I'm from Monthly Football.\nCan I interview you?
Uh... This is a bit sudden...
Brushing me off? How rude!
I want to write for Eleven, too...
Hey, we locked eyes.\nWanna tussle or what?
Great... just what I needed.
Not bad... for a middle schooler.\nI'll let you slide today.
Wha—! I was just goofing off!\nI'm not lonely!
Dig in, don't be shy!
Whew, that was some prime slurping!
Get ready for my magnum opus!
Impressive, <FST:UNMEI>!\nYou've got a champion's appetite!
Dig in while it's piping hot!
Liked it?\nDoor's always open!
Ramen's like rocket fuel for footballers!
Come back hungry, ya hear!
Sure, it's a sports clash. But\nalso a test of ideals and skill.
Can't risk making the wrong call\nif I want to complete the club.
According to my read, there's no\nline of play that excludes me.
If you prioritize foresight,\nI'm indispensable.
Time to show you\nhow I bulldoze through!
Charge me head-on!\nI'll take it full force!
<FUL:BENTEN>—taking the stage!
Counting on you.
Let the curtain rise.
If you want your illusion to\ntruly shine... you'll need me.
A challenge? Fine.\nI'll answer them all.
I hope you choose wisely.
You gonna try and climb ME?
I wanna join your climb—\nto the top of football.
I'll do my best to show\nwhat I'm capable of!
Choose me, and I'll do\nanything in my power to help!
Allow me to demonstrate\ntrue elegance.
I trust you'll make a choice\nbefitting your refinement.
Dosukoi! Thought I'd step into\nthe ring they call football!
From sumo ring to football pitch—\n<FUL:MAKUSHITA>'s here to win!
I'll show you my blade in action!
The way of the sword...\nI wanna entrust it to you.
Behold the full depth of my\ndevotion, my long-awaited Master!
My fate is yours. All rests upon\nthe will of my Master's heart.
Time to crank up the rock.\nWatch and learn.
Later, losers!
I want you to judge\nthe worth of my metal.
Whether this metal shines...\nthat's on you.
I want ya to see how far\nmy rice balls can take us!
How 'bout we whip up a\nbig ol' rice ball together?
Think you can ride this\nbig wave called me?
Pick me, and you're riding the\nbiggest wave your team's ever seen!
その[程度/ていど]で[指導/しどう]されないと\nいけないんですか？
その[制服/せいふく]の[着方/きかた]…　[指導対象/しどうたいしょう]だ！　\nボタンは[全部閉/ぜんぶし]めろ！
[相手/あいて]は　[社会/しゃかい]のゴミです。\nぶちのめして[掃除/そうじ]をしましょう。
[中坊/ちゅうぼう]が[調子/ちょうし]に[乗/の]るんじゃねえ！\n[昨日/きのう]の[借/か]りを[返/かえ]してやるぜ！
Remember, you asked for this.\nWe're not gonna hold back.
Sure, it's a sports clash. But\nalso a test of ideals and skill.
A challenge? Fine.\nI'll answer them all.
I hope you choose wisely.
